quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  86,1,aqsm allah subhanah balsma' walnajm aldhy ytrq laylana wama 'adrak ma eizam hdha alnjm? hu alnajm almudi' almtwhhij. ma kulu nafs 'iilaa 'awkal biha malak raqib yahfaz ealayha 'aemalaha lthasb ealayha yawm alqyamt
  86,2,aqsm allah subhanah balsma' walnajm aldhy ytrq laylana wama 'adrak ma eizam hdha alnjm? hu alnajm almudi' almtwhhij. ma kulu nafs 'iilaa 'awkal biha malak raqib yahfaz ealayha 'aemalaha lthasb ealayha yawm alqyamt
  86,3,aqsm allah subhanah balsma' walnajm aldhy ytrq laylana wama 'adrak ma eizam hdha alnjm? hu alnajm almudi' almtwhhij. ma kulu nafs 'iilaa 'awkal biha malak raqib yahfaz ealayha 'aemalaha lthasb ealayha yawm alqyamt
  86,4,aqsm allah subhanah balsma' walnajm aldhy ytrq laylana wama 'adrak ma eizam hdha alnjm? hu alnajm almudi' almtwhhij. ma kulu nafs 'iilaa 'awkal biha malak raqib yahfaz ealayha 'aemalaha lthasb ealayha yawm alqyamt
  86,5,"flynzr al'iinsan almunkar llbeth mimm khuliqa? liyaelam 'an 'iieadat khalq al'iinsan laysat aseb mn khalaqah awwla khalaq min mny mnsbb bsret fi alrhm, yakhruj min bayn sulb alrajul wsdr almra. 'iina aladhi khalaq al'iinsan min hdha alma' laqadr ealaa rajeih 'iilaa alhayat baed almwt"
  86,6,"falyanzur al'iinsan almunkar llbeth mimm khuliqa? liyaelam 'an 'iieadat khalq al'iinsan laysat aseb mn khalaqah awwla khalaq min mny mnsbb bsret fi alrhm, yakhruj min bayn sulb alrajul wsdr almra. 'iina aladhi khalaq al'iinsan min hdha alma' laqadr ealaa rajeih 'iilaa alhayat baed almwt"
  86,7,"flynzr al'iinsan almunkar llbeth mimm khuliqa? liyaelam 'an 'iieadat khalq al'iinsan laysat aseb mn khalaqah awwla khalaq min mny mnsbb bsret fi alrhm, yakhruj min bayn sulb alrajul wsdr almra. 'iina aladhi khalaq al'iinsan min hdha alma' laqadr ealaa rajeih 'iilaa alhayat baed almwt"
  86,8,"flynzr al'iinsan almunkar llbeth mimm khuliqa? liyaelam 'an 'iieadat khalq al'iinsan laysat aseb mn khalaqah awwla khalaq min mny mnsbb bsret fi alrhm, yakhruj min bayn sulb alrajul wsdr almra. 'iina aladhi khalaq al'iinsan min hdha alma' laqadr ealaa rajeih 'iilaa alhayat baed almwt"
  86,9,"ywm tukhtabr alsarayir fima akhfth, wyumayaz alsaalih minha min alfasd, fama lil'iinsan min quat yadfae biha ean nfsh, wama lah min nasir yadfae eanh eadhab allh"
  86,10,"ywm tukhtabr alsarayir fima akhfth, wyumayaz alsaalih minha min alfasd, fama lil'iinsan min quat yadfae biha ean nfsh, wama lah min nasir yadfae eanh eadhab allh"
  86,11,"walsma' dhat almatar almtkrr, wal'ard dhat altshqq bima ytkhllha min nbat, 'iina alquran laqawl fasl bayn alhaqu walbatl, wama hu balhzl. wala yajuz llmkhlwq 'an yuqsim bighayr allh, wa'illa faqad ashrk"
  86,12,"walsma' dhat almatar almtkrr, wal'ard dhat altshqq bima ytkhllha min nbat, 'iina alquran laqawl fasl bayn alhaqu walbatl, wama hu balhzl. wala yajuz llmkhlwq 'an yuqsim bighayr allh, wa'illa faqad ashrk"
  86,13,"walsma' dhat almatar almtkrr, wal'ard dhat altshqq bima ytkhllha min nbat, 'iina alquran laqawl fasl bayn alhaqu walbatl, wama hu balhzl. wala yajuz llmkhlwq 'an yuqsim bighayr allh, wa'illa faqad ashrk"
  86,14,"walsama' dhat almatar almtkrr, wal'ard dhat altshqq bima ytkhllha min nbat, 'iina alquran laqawl fasl bayn alhaqu walbatl, wama hu balhzl. wala yajuz llmkhlwq 'an yuqsim bighayr allh, wa'illa faqad ashrk"
  86,15,"'in almukadhibin llrswl salaa allah ealayh wslm, wllqran, yakidun wydbrwn; lydfeu bkydhm alhaqu wywydu albatl, wa'akid kydana l'izhar alhq, walaw karih alkafrwn, fala tastaejil lahum -ayha alrswl- bitalab 'iinzal aleiqab bhm, bal 'amhilhum wanzrhm qalilana wala tastaejil lhm, wstra ma yhll bihim min aleadhab walnkal waleqwbt walhlak"
  86,16,"'in almukadhibin llrswl salaa allah ealayh wslm, wllqran, yakidun wydbrwn; lydfeu bkydhm alhaqu wywydu albatl, wa'akid kydana l'izhar alhq, walaw karih alkafrwn, fala tastaejil lahum -ayha alrswl- bitalab 'iinzal aleiqab bhm, bal 'amhilhum wanzrhm qalilana wala tastaejil lhm, wstra ma yhll bihim min aleadhab walnkal waleqwbt walhlak"
  86,17,"'in almukadhibin llrswl salaa allah ealayh wslm, wllqran, yakidun wydbrwn; lydfeu bkydhm alhaqu wywydu albatl, wa'akid kydana l'izhar alhq, walaw karih alkafrwn, fala tastaejil lahum -ayha alrswl- bitalab 'iinzal aleiqab bhm, bal 'amhilhum wanzrhm qalilana wala tastaejil lhm, wstra ma yhll bihim min aleadhab walnkal waleqwbt walhlak"